Yvonne Imoh-Abasi Glory Ekwere (amụrụ na ubochi nke ato na onwa Machị ,1987), nke a maara dịka Yvonne Vixen Ekwere, bụ onye mgbasa ozi Naijiria, onye na-emepụta ọdịnaya na onye na-eme ihe nkiri nke na-arụ ọrụ dị ka onye na-eweta E-Weekly na Ihe ngosi onyonyo silverbird  Kemgbe ọ malitere dị ka onye na-akwado ihe ngosi n'abalị na Rhythm 93.7 FM, ụdị ngosi ya ahụla ka o meriri ọtụtụ ihe nrite.

Vixen bụ nwa afọ Akwa Ibom Steeti, Nigeria, mana a mụrụ ya dị ka nwa ikpeazụ n'ime ụmụ asaa na Lagos Steeti, Ndida odida anyanwu Nijiria ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Ulo akwukwo praimari airforce  Victoria Island, Lagos na Holy Child College, Lagos n'otu n'otu. O nwere nzere bachelọ na History na International Studies nke o nwetara na Mahadum lagos Steeti

Ọrụ ya malitere n'afọ 2008 mgbe Ikponmwosa Osakioduwa kpọrọ ya ka ọ bụrụ onye na-akwado ihe ngosi redio a na-akpọ Dance Party nke na-egosi na Rhythm 93.7 FM. Vixen mechara nyochaa ma merie ọrụ dị ka onye na-egosi ihe ngosi ntụrụndụ nke Ihe igwe onyonyo silverbirdbụ E-Weekly Ọrụ ya ahụla ajụjụ ọnụ ya na ndị ama ama ama ma na-akwado ọtụtụ ihe omume dị elu gụnyere nwa agbogho kacha maa mma n’afo 2012 na onye bụbu onye isi ala, Goodluck Jonathan's "Nri abali na ndi metutara show biz "n'etiti ndị ọzọ. N'ọnwa Ọktọba afọ 2015, ọ malitere ihe ngosi nke ya nke akpọrọ Drive Time with Vixen
O hotara Oprah Winfrey dị ka isi iyi nke mkpali ya.
O meela ihe nkiri ma pụta na ihe nkiri na ihe nkiri ncha gụnyere 7 Inch Curve, Render to Caesar, Put a Ring on It na oge 2 nke Gidi Up ebe ọ pụtara na ihe omume ato.
